[0.198, "o", "\r\n>> \u001b[32;1minstall\u001b[0m   Confirm configuration\r\nDatabase host       localhost\r\nDatabase port       3306\r\nDatabase name       atom\r\nDatabase user       atom\r\nDatabase password   1234\r\nSearch host         localhost\r\nSearch port         9200\r\nSearch index        atom\r\nSite title          AtoM\r\nSite description    Access to Memory\r\nSite base URL       http://127.0.0.1\r\nAdmin email         ikhsanadzni@gmail.com\r\nAdmin username      sansan\r\nAdmin password      12345\r\n\u001b[30;46m                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[30;46m  Confirm configuration and continue? (y/N)  \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[30;46m                                             \u001b[0m\r\n"]
